text: LaToya Cantrell (born April 3, 1972) is an American politician. She is the mayor of New Orleans, Louisiana since 2018. She is a member of the Democratic Party. Cantrell has represented District B on the New Orleans City Council. ==References== ==Other websites== * New Orleans City Council member profile Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Mayors of New Orleans Category:Politicians from Los Angeles Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:African-American politicians
